<h3 id="intro">Intro</h3>
<p>
  Today, my beloved Lenovo P14s Gen 1 had a "computer 
  says noooooo" moment. Since purchasing this machine 
  6 months ago, it has been rock solid.
  Then, out of the blue it hits me with a rotating 
  carousel of full screen colours: red, blue, green, 
  white and black. 
</p>

<p>
  OMG! This is my work laptop and I dont have a spare.
  I tried holding the power button down to force a reboot 
  but that did not help. I was met with the same series of 
  flashy flashy.
</p>

<p>
  <i>I am Jack's cold sweat.</i>
</p>

<h3 id="the-crime-scene">The Crime Scene</h3>
<p>
  The GIF below shows what I was dealing with.
</p>

